Program: The Forum
Title: Making Good Law
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01568lw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Mar 2013
As post-revolutionary societies across the Arab world grapple with the task of creating new legal frameworks, Bridget Kendall brings together three prominent international lawyers to look at the challenges: former candidate for presidency in Lebanon and human rights lawyer Chibli Mallat; Shlomit Wallerstein, fellow in criminal law from Oxford University; and leading international lawyer Philippe Sands. PHOTO: Lady Justice (BBC) Show less